      "role": "user",
      "content": "I finally made it to the edge of the Grand Canyon. It's... it's everything I thought it would be. Huge. Silent. I've spent my whole life trying to reach these points on a map, but now that I'm actually here, it just feels like I’ve reached the end of the line. Like there aren't any more miles left in me.",
